Text-Todo-Simple

Text::Todo::Simple is a simple and basic todo list manager, without all
the additional features that make people spending more time on organizing
tasks instead of completing them.

Text::Todo::Simple tries to be as effective as possible doing the unique
thing it does without any surplus.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Text::Todo::Simple

You can also look for information at:

    GitHub page
        http://github.com/AlexBio/Text-Todo-Simple

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Text-Todo-Simple

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Text-Todo-Simple

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Text-Todo-Simple

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Text-Todo-Simple/


